dialogue: So anyway... this tunnel leads somewhere really special. If I'm honest, I don't really think you're ready for it just yet.
It's not that I don't want you to go, but... well, it might be irresponsible of me to let you through right now.
If you want to come back later, when you got a bit more air under your wings, I might consider letting you in.
Hmmm... lets say you can come back when you have free'd a bunch of fireflies. That seems like a good test to make sure you're ready.
